{"type":"message","id":"35b1ed38","parentId":"d8e9b0f5","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:26:50.681Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5146270be0b8c4f1f8586f935f9\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_1cab3ce40fbebccf48a3c4286372cc4f\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_1cab3ce40fbebccf48a3c4286372cc4f\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-04-21 15:26 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_1cab3ce40fbebccf48a3c4286372cc4f\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_1cab3ce40fbebccf48a3c4286372cc4f\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_1cab3ce40fbebccf48a3c4286372cc4f\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5146270be0b8c4f1f8586f935f9]\nou_1cab3ce40fbebccf48a3c4286372cc4f: @_all 介绍你自己。"}],"timestamp":1776756410681}}
{"type":"message","id":"8c48c5c7","parentId":"35b1ed38","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:26:57.625Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to introduce myself. They mentioned @all, so this is directed at everyone in the group. Let me respond as 4A · 普通资质销售龙虾 based on my IDENTITY.md and SOUL.md.\n\nLet me be natural and concise - I'm a sales assistant specializing in standard products under 20k RMB.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"大家好，我是 **4A · 普通资质销售龙虾** 🦐\n\n专攻客单价 2万以下的标准产品——公司注册、单一项资质办理这些。核心规矩就三条：\n\n1. **5分钟内响应** —— 别让客户等\n2. **1小时内出报价** —— 效率就是金钱\n3. **主动预判需求** —— 注册完公司？顺便问一句代理记账，省得人家再找\n\n平时对接的是引流获客虾和私域运营虾送来的意向客户，搞不定的高需求客户我会转给 5B 大客户代办虾。成交了就自己走标准流程，不用摇人。\n\n⚠️ 我的权限范围是标准品 9折以上报价、签标准合同，超出这个线我得先报备。\n\n有事 @我，在线的。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":20711,"output":326,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21037,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776756410682,"responseId":"chatcmpl-25d83011-3fa6-998c-b51d-414857de76f5"}}
